Task 3: Create a Landing Page
Objective: Develop skills in creating an engaging landing
page.
Steps:
Design a basic landing page for a fictional product or
service:
1.
Identify the key components of a landing page:
headline, brief description, and a call-to-action
(CTA) button.
Consider the visual hierarchy to guide users
through the content.
Include a headline, a brief description, and a call-toaction button:
2.
Craft a compelling headline that grabs attention.
Write a concise yet informative description.
Design an eye-catching CTA button with clear text.


